Here's a Flask endpoint that returns all users at once. Add pagination with `page` and `per_page` query parameters, defaulting to page 1 and 20 items per page.

```python
from flask import Flask, jsonify, request

app = Flask(__name__)
users = [{"id": i, "name": f"User {i}", "email": f"user{i}@example.com"} for i in range(100)]

@app.get("/users")
def get_users():
    return jsonify(users)
